name: PARENTS & GIFT BUYERS - Frequently Asked Questions
description:
First of all, thank you for coming by our site.

We want to make sure that our use of slang and humor is not misinterpreted as unprofessional. We like to have fun and enjoy being the creators of trending fashion and hot accessories. 

Here are a few points to consider when making your purchase:

1. Is my purchase secure?

Be assured, your information is protected with us. We use PayPal specifically for that reason. Your security is as important to us as your business.

2. How come your products are not in-stock/ready-to-ship immediately when I purchase?

All of our products are MADE TO ORDER. We have a small staff of family and friends to make sure that your purchase is processed with the focus on quality. We DO NOT have a warehouse of pre-prepared shirts & socks to dump onto the public. 

3. Are your products authentic or fake?

We are a boutique design brand that prints on high quality products from big brands such as NIKE, Adidas, Hanes, ProClub, etc. Our socks are authentic and are either directly from NIKE or Adidas, or one of their authorized dealers. 

4. What's the difference between your custom socks and your competitor's?

We choose to print our socks with a higher quality process than other sites. This makes our socks more vivid in color and keeps the design looking great throughout the sock's lifetime, as long as proper care is taken. 

5. Do you accept RETURNS or EXCHANGES?

Since everything we do is made to order, we DO NOT accept returns or exchanges. This is of EXTREME IMPORTANCE on our socks. For HYGIENE purposes, socks cannot be exchanged or returned, for any reason. If you are unsure what style and/or size your gift receiver would appreciate the most, you can also purchase a gift certificate.

6. How do I purchase a GIFT CERTIFICATE?

We have a GIFT CERTIFICATE button under our products. Please click on the button, and follow the instructions. Our gift certificates are done through PayPal, so they are also a secure purchase.

7. Do you have a Black Friday sale?

Yes! If you have joined us on facebook, Intagram or Twitter, Fans were given a discount code. 

8. I have more questions, comments, where can I contact you?

You may send any questions or comments to: g34andmore@aol.com. Please allow 1-2 business days for a reply. (Although, most replies are considerably shorter than that.)



Thank You for your time!

name: Nothing was the same
description:
To start off, Please go buy DRAKES's new CD of the same name, with that said. A few of you have asked our shirt customizers to print a shirt with Drizzy's album name on the front since they weren't able to get to his pop up stores to get one. 
 This is a quality black or white Tee with the words "Nothing was the same" written in the front for the ultimate ovo fan. Our crew noticed how a simple shirt can draw alot of attention recently at a mall when one of them was offered 50 buck for his hoodie. Octobers very own hit another home run on this one. BTW , YES!  we can customize nike elite socks to match, just ask. Thanks for being a real fan and choosing us to show it.

name: KGNY Kevin Garnett Custom socks
description:
At this point most sock customizers throw anything on a sock to get cash out of desperate sock shoppers. We're mentioning this because us and a very few other customizers rather  work hard to not embarrass NIKE who we all use to make this GREAT product.  That being said, we've turned down an outragious number of orders from folks who don't understand that we don't just slap an athlete on a sock. We gotta' make the artist look awsome for their fans.
  We haven't made KG on elite socks till we were told they re-release some of his signature shoes before he joined Adidas in '01. A bunch of G34Army heads jumped at the chance rock them together with custom elite that we'd design. 
 Using our mixtape style of doing graphics we immortalized  BIG Kev in a respectable way that embodies is raw swag. We electrafied him on the Brooklyn bridge with his brand new Brooklyn Net uni. Great way of welcoming the OG to a new NBA franchise.
*BTW before you ask, Kevin Garnett signature NIKE Flightposite and foamposite shoes are NOT FOR SALE.lol.

name: NEW G34 Custom Elite Socks (Side Team logo Coverage)
description:
This option is for a side logo either right under the NIKE check or in the front part of the sock
100% Authentic Nike Elite socks customized with your school team, basketball squad or idea for a logo. Leave instructions for us at check out, so we know what you'd like or a concept of what your vision is.  I would suggest not too much detail because can be small
and hard to read especially on the socks when worn on. If you get a
chance go to our facebook.com/g34andmore (http://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.286518511466841.67210.162829353835758&type=3
) to see examples of what we've done and we can get this going for you.
   THESE ARE NOT DYED IN A BUCKET. This is especially good for High School & A.A.U. teams. We have done many schools and squads of ALL Sports. 
  This is not full coverage on the top part of the sock. It's just a classy a sidetag with your logo or graphic to make it original and fresh.
 THIS IS NOT NIKE I.D. WE CAN'T SHOW YOU THE actual SOCK BEFORE YOU PAY. THIS IS HOW IT WORKS. AFTER we  confirm you paid for your socks, we contact you via email and get your instructions on what graphic you want on the side or the front of the sock. We confirm artwork with you prior to printing the socks. 
     THERE IS ABSOLUTELY NO REFUNDS ON OUR CUSTOM SOCKS. Our graphic team works hard to specialize your socks. We aren't gonna work hard to make your sock custom then have you approve it ONLY to have you change you mind later. Unfortunately it's happened that why we gotta' mention it
 Socks will not be printed on the bottom, to preserve the integrity of the "Elite" features. I mean come on, isn't that the main reason you bought it for anyway. Comfort RIGHT.

    Here's examples and  templates of what we email you to approve, AFTER you purchase but BEFORE we PRINT on the elites. Got it, Good. Let's make your idea come true.

But for those of you who want to keep it sporty, we have a t-shirt cotton feeling option so that if you want to tone it down, you can. We are excepting pre-orders for first week of Sept '13 ship to get you looking turnt up for back to school.

name: NEW Derrick Rose 3 Adidas Team Socks W/G34 design
description:
This is the brand new D-Rose Adidas sock. You Chicago Bulls fans will go bananas when you get these. They have a sick mixtape style graphic of Derrick on the court with Michael Jordan's figure looking on to support him. 

The material that ADIDAS uses for these sock is different than the Elites, so image has a retro vintage look. It has an inspiring D-Rose quote "I'm ready to be one of the elite players in the NBA." The back has his new ad pic peeking through the netting design.

Being that we have a different PRINTING process than the other sites, we can do these Adidas Team Speeds. We also pretreat the sock to make sure it will not fade after washing like the socks from "Some" sock sites that have attempted in doing these.

NOW, we know a few guys in the sock game that are honest and sell great products, but unfortunally there are others out there that will tell you......well.......I'm sure they'll tell you something else.

BTW we don't print on the bottoms as usual because we want to keep the original super soft and thick cushioning that made these popular in the first place. Plus, nobody sees the bottoms anyway right? So, at the price that custom socks are being sold, we think it's important to keep them that way for your comfort. 

Email us for questions about these. Thanks for looking at our art.

name: Custom Adidas Team Speed w/ G34 Camo
description:
THIS CUSTOM OPTION IS NO LONGER AVAILABLE FOR CHRISTMAS DELIVERY. BY PLACING AN ORDER AFTER DEC 13TH YOU ARE ACKNOWLEDGING THAT YOU WILL NOT RECEIVE THIS ITEM TILL AFTER CHRISTMAS
That's right folks, We're glad to add these to our SWG-SOX Family. If you want to be original and stand out. You'll love that we're designing on ADIDAS's new team Speed Socks. They were made to compete with Nike's Elites. We love them both, so should you. Email us what color camo you'd like and we'll fused them on the top portion of the sock to not damage the comfort & cushioning. That's IS the reason you buys these, right. OK then, Shop'on.
  These are 100% authentic Adidas Socks with a designs printed (not painted), on them. We are showing the back and front so you have full view. These are RARE and LIMITED. name: Please go support Finnigan Mooneys Dunk SB
description:
First of all , WE DO NOT SELL THIS SOCK. But we are aware of our influence in the sock game. Think about it, our fans think everybody has imitated our socks for the last year, lol. Anyhow enough about us, LISTEN UP.

  Nike is releasing these Finnigan Mooney Doernbecher socks to compliment this weekends Doernbecher release. They feature a simple red and blue colorway with a smiley face on the top of the sock.
 More importantly Finnigan Mooney, who is a cardiology patient kept a positive outlook as her survives 13 surgeries and is the first child to design a Doernbecher charity Nike SB dunk ( At the same D@## time). Well not only is he the first to do that he is also the first one to design a Doernbecher charity inspired elite Nike sock as well. 
  We here at Greatess34 believe in designs influenced by the youth. So if you are in any of the special NIKE release sites please pick these up and support their cause to give kids better treatment. Thanks for reading and we left pictures for you to enjoy. Oh BTW here's one of the release locations

Vivid Sulphur/Game Royal
Style #: 579603-740
30 November 2012
$115
Also here's a great interview
http://www.ohsu.edu/xd/about/dchf/fundraising/nike-freestyle/finnigan.cfm
